<<< INSTALL perfume/pmacs package >>>

1. Extract downloaded binary package in any directory you want to install.
   (ex) If you install in your home directory.

	cd $HOME
	tar xvzf pmacs-install.tar.gz

2. Enter package directory.

	cd pmacs-install

3. Execute installer

	./install.sh

4. Set the shell environment variable PATH

	(ex) PATH=${PATH}:${HOME}/pmacs-install/bin

5. Execute pmacs editor

	pmacs

#eof
